      "content": "wait seriously?? i don't feel any pain though. it doesn't even hurt, just feels a bit muffled like i'm underwater or something. i'm in oslo and it's pretty late, i don't really want to go to the hospital just for an ear thing if it's not actually hurting. do you think it's really that urgent if there's no pain?",
